# PaymentCardReaderStore.StoreError.passcodeDisabled

**Case**

To fetch a batch device’s passcode needs to be enabled.

## Declaration

```swift
case passcodeDisabled
```

## Discussion

Your app needs to ask the user to set a security passcode on their device.
